                    <h2 class="mt-2">Overview</h2>
                    <p>As UX/UI capability lead, I led the creation of our DXC UX process within the New Orleans Digital Transformation Center. This allowed our team to align on common practices to become unified in our method. The goal was to evangelize the UX process both internally and externally to gain awareness and secure projects for the team.</p>
