                <div class="col-lg-8 mb-0 mb-lg-2">
                    <h2>UX Definition</h2>
                    <p>We <strong>visually design</strong> digital experiences based on a<strong> deep understanding</strong> of the users   and the business strategic objectives. We<strong> validate</strong> these designs through usability testing and<strong> iterate</strong> based on user feedback.</p>
                </div>

