                    <div class="col-lg-8 mb-0 mb-lg-2 mt-4">
                        <h2>DXC UX Process</h2>
                        <p><strong>Discover - </strong> The initial phase of our process of discovery, we focus on understanding the needs of the users. We also aid in the defining of the problem using design thinking methodology.</p>
                        <p><strong>Design - </strong> We solution based on the painpoints discovered and present many variations of wireframes to the stakeholders working with the development team. We get stakeholder approvals on high fidelity wireframes before handoff to development.</p>
                        <p><strong>Develop & Deploy - </strong> We then assist the build of the designs. We work alongside development in asset creation and oversee the UI design quality. We also use this time validate assumptions with users.</p>
                    </div>

